{
  "texts": [
    "The newest iteration, Med-PaLM2, was introduced at Google Health's annual event, in March 2023.",
    "It was developed based on PaLM2, the language model underlying the Google chatbot, Bard that adopted different models over time, beginning with LaMDA followed by PaLM2, and finally Gemini Pro.",
    "For training researchers implemented a collection of text datasets from the internet.",
    "This corpus included various sources, such as articles, books, websites, and other textual content.",
    "Concerning performance, the model demonstrated a level of expertise comparable to that of a human expert in answering the U.S. Medical Licensing Examination (USMLE)-style questions."
  ]
}